<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef8d8a6b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2710"><num value="2710">§ 2710.</num><heading> Applicability of provisions to amendments to orders</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this chapter applicable to orders shall be applicable to amendments to orders.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef8d8a6c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/93/428/s11">Pub. L. 93–428, § 11</ref>, <date date="1974-10-01">Oct. 1, 1974</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/1176">88 Stat. 1176</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
